Package: nemo-git-integration
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         nemo (>= 3.0),
         git,
         jq,
         zenity,
         coreutils,
         sed,
         findutils
Recommends: python3-nemo
Suggests: gitk, git-gui
Description: Git integration for Nemo file manager
 Integrate Git directly into the Nemo file explorer via context menus.
 .
 Perform common Git operations without opening a terminal or IDE:
  - Initialize, clone, and manage branches
  - View status, log, and fetch updates
  - Pull, add, commit, and push changes
  - Reset and undo operations
 .
 Tested primarily on Linux Mint Debian Edition and other
 Debian-based distributions using Cinnamon/Nemo.
